OL,3,CLondon Underground strikes: Tube
OL,4,Cdrivers to walk out in dispute over
OL,5,Chours
OL,7,FHowever, these proposals have been
OL,8,Frejected by the majority of staff,
OL,9,Famid concerns about shift lengths,
OL,10,Funacceptable working time
OL,11,Farrangements, as well as the potential
OL,12,Fimpact on fatigue and safety.
OL,14,FThe union says the plans are being
OL,15,Fpushed ahead as attempts to resolve
OL,16,Fthe dispute were not successful.
OL,18,FAround 1,800 of union members were
OL,19,Finvolved in the dispute over the
OL,20,Fintroduction of a compressed four-day
OL,21,Fworking week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
