OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1773223748
OL,3,CLondon Underground strikes: Tube
OL,4,Cdrivers to walk out in dispute over
OL,5,Chours
OL,7,FEddie Dempsey, RMT General Secretary,
OL,8,Fsaid: "London Underground is trying to
OL,9,Fforce through major changes to working
OL,10,Fpatterns that have already been
OL,11,Frejected by our members.
OL,13,F"We are clear that these proposals
OL,14,Fraise serious concerns around fatigue,
OL,15,Fsafety and work-life balance.
OL,17,F"Despite our best efforts over many
OL,18,Fmonths, no satisfactory outcome has
OL,19,Fbeen reached so we have no choice but
OL,20,Fto call strike dates.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
